(19,1,E'train',E'Batumi - Tblisi',E'Train to Tblisi',E'I love trains. There is something very special about staring out of the window of a train and seeing the landscape slowly pass by. I feel like I\'m slowly starting to be a "train rider expert" if thats a phrase. Last year I did the entire trans-mongolian express starting in Beijing all the way to Helsinki. (read more here!). Reading about trains i was expecting a soviet style train. but it was a super modern train. Aircon, power plugs, nice seats everything.',E'2019-08-27 09:00:00+00',E'2019-08-27 03:00:00+00',E'Pretty exciting to check out the capital to be honest. along the way I have heard great stories about Tblisi. ',NULL,E'2019-11-17 11:27:30.299498+00',E'POLYGON((41.649492 41.64432,41.649492 42.204874,44.799719 42.204874,44.799719 41.64432,41.649492 41.64432))'),
