(56,16,E'place',E'Hong Kong Airport',E'A small start to a big journey',E'Just landed in Hong Kong after 15 hours of flying! Worth it though. The weather is already a lot better then in the UK! Looking forward to seeing the city!\n\n![](https://storage.googleapis.com/jeroen-travel-images/30242c7019d1526a755175e5568f0aace5df19f540394d77-IMG_0170.JPG)\n\n![](https://storage.googleapis.com/jeroen-travel-images/335adfd6d0875a44e989941c1ffb8f1032080c95f3788b7a-IMG_0173.JPG)',E'2018-05-25 00:00:00+00',E'2018-05-26 12:00:00+00',E'Just landed in Hong Kong after 15 hours of flying. Very excited to start, but also slightly anxious. ',NULL,E'2020-04-19 14:56:16.263965+00',NULL),
