(58,16,E'trip',E'Hong Kong Island',E'Lion Rock and buddhist temple',E'Today we climbed up the Lion Rock mountain, and again found some stunning views! It’s incredible how many people can be cramped up in this tiny area! On the way we passed by a Chinese temple as well ⛩',E'2018-05-27 00:00:00+00',E'2018-05-27 00:00:00+00',E'Today we climbed up the Lion Rock mountain, and again found some stunning views! It’s incredible how many people can be cramped up in this tiny area! On the way we passed by a Chinese temple as well ⛩',NULL,E'2020-04-26 10:00:18.441809+00',NULL),
