(60,16,E'place',E'Guangzhou',E'Entering mainland China',E' This morning we took the bus from Hong Kong to Guangzhou which is in mainland China. Once we arrived we took the metro to the Canton Tower. This city has some really cool looking architecture!! Also managed to get an egg puff filled with vanilla ice and Oreos in some really wacky mall! It tasted outta this world 🏆',E'2018-05-30 00:00:00+00',E'2018-05-30 00:00:00+00',E'Today we are leaving Hong Kong and entering the Chinese People Republic. ',NULL,E'2020-04-26 10:00:18.441809+00',E'POLYGON((113.25618 22.313693,113.25618 23.13228,114.164385 23.13228,114.164385 22.313693,113.25618 22.313693))'),
(61,16,E'place',E'Yangshou',E'Amazing natural beauty',E'First full day in Yangshuo, and so far, it’s really great! The scenery is literally straight out of a movie! We rented a bike today and just spend the day cycling through the landscape. In the evening we did have to cross a couple of rivers with the bike, which was a bit of an adventure, but definitely worth it!',E'2018-06-01 00:00:00+00',E'2018-06-01 00:00:00+00',E' This day was filled with adventure. The scenery also looks like its literally straight out of a movie',NULL,E'2020-04-26 10:37:22.858233+00',NULL),
(62,16,E'trip',E'Yangshou',E'Taking biking to the next level',E'We decided to rent the bike again, and go to see the ancient stone village, about 18km away. This turned out to be an awful decision since 90% of the ride was uphill. Pfff, you don’t wish that upon your worst enemy! Sweating like crazy haha :) Anyway, the ride itself was nice and the stone village was OK as well (not worth the ride though!)',E'2018-06-02 00:00:00+00',E'2018-06-02 00:00:00+00',E'Today we decided to rent the bike again. It turned out to be a bad descision. ',NULL,E'2020-04-26 10:37:22.858233+00',NULL),
(63,16,E'place',E'Zhangjiajie',E'Some sleeping, Some planning',E'This morning we arrived at Zhangjiajie, since I didn’t sleep very well on the train I decided to do a quick nap in between. As a result we didn’t do a lot today expect from kind of planning out what the plan is after China and how we’re getting into Mongolia and Russia. Tomorrow we plan on entering the nature party though, which should be very nice!',E'2018-06-04 00:00:00+00',E'2018-06-04 00:00:00+00',E'To tired to do much today. We planned the next few days, and ofcourse ate food! :) ',NULL,E'2020-04-26 10:37:22.858233+00',NULL),
(64,16,E'trip',E'Zhangjiajie Nature reserve',E'The amazing Zhangjiajie nature',E'Today we entered the Zhangjiajie National Park, which is also a UNESCO site. The photos don’t really do justice to the enormous mountainous landscape and the extreme beauty of this park! We spend the whole day walking along a route and haven’t nearly seen everything yet! Looking forward to spend more time here tomorrow!',E'2018-06-05 00:00:00+00',E'2018-06-05 00:00:00+00',E'Walking our asses off today, but its worth it!',NULL,E'2020-04-26 10:39:01.211431+00',NULL),
(65,16,E'trip',E'Zhangjiajie Nature reserve',E'Still as stunning as yesterday',E'Today our second day in the National Park, and we decided to walk another path available. Which resulted in more beautiful scenery. Tomorrow we’ll have a look at the other side of the park which promises to be very nice as well. ',E'2018-06-06 00:00:00+00',E'2018-06-06 00:00:00+00',E'Today our second day in the National Park, and we decided to walk another path available.',NULL,E'2020-04-26 10:44:53.163585+00',NULL),
(66,16,E'place',E'Chengdu City Center',E'Chengdu',E'We arrived in the morning in Chengdu, after having slept a lot better than the previous night on a night train. After checking in at our Hostel, we walked around a bit looking for breakfast (which was, again, very good! 😊). Then we proceed to go for a bigger walk, wandering around the city. Since this is the city of Pandas (apparently the only area where there are still wild pandas) they make good use of it and every street corners sells pandas related souvenirs. Later in the day we ended up in a Taoism temple which was also quite impressive! Tomorrow we’ll try to get to the panda research centre to see some pandas in real life!',E'2018-06-09 00:00:00+00',E'2018-06-09 00:00:00+00',E'Our first day in Chengdu is spend roaming around the city, taking it all in.',NULL,E'2020-04-26 10:44:53.163585+00',NULL),
